data.description: Welcome home to this charming three bedroom three bathroom all brick ranch nestled in the center of the highly sought after neighborhood of Carrington Green located just minutes from Five Forks. Built in 1994, this single owner traditional home has been immaculately maintained and zoned for some of the top schools in the state.  Priced right and ready to move, this one won’t last long in this market!
